TEXT.TITLE: KRAFT <KRA> COMPLETES ACQUISITION
TEXT.BODY: Kraft Inc said it completed the acquisition of Holleb and Co, a foodservice distributor based in Bensenville, Ill. Terms were withheld. It said Holleb's 1986 sales were about 85 mln dlrs. Reuter
